title: Jesus Heals
author: Hopsoplo
pages:
#- A man with leprosy came to him on his knees, "If you are willing, you can make me clean." Filled with compassion, Jesus reached out his hand and touched the man. "I am willing," he said, "Be clean!" Immediately the leprosy left him and he was cured. Jesus
#- away at once with a warning: "See that you don't tell this to anyone. But go, show yourself to the priest and offer the sacrifices that Moses commanded for your cleansing as a testimony to them."
#- 